headline: S&P Global Schedules First Quarter 2025 Earnings Announcement and Conference Call for Tuesday, April 29, 2025
summary: S&P Global's (NYSE: SPGI) first quarter 2025 results will be issued on Tuesday, April 29, 2025 via news release at approximately 7:15 a.m. Eastern Daylight Time. The news release will be available at www.spglobal.com.
